response.original_title: Mary Chapin Carpenter: Jubilee: Live at Wolf Trap
response.overview: Mary Chapin Carpenter, one of the most intelligent and soulful voices in contemporary country music, is captured onstage in this 1995 concert video that features duets with Shawn Colvin and Joan Baez. Interviews with Chapin and other artists complement her music. Songs include "I Feel Lucky," "Passionate Kisses," "He Thinks He'll Keep Her," "Why Walk When You Can Fly," "Down at the Twist and Shout" and "Jubilee."
